OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm and
OL,6,Fsunny evening. Staying clear
OL,7,Fovernight, but the risk of some
OL,8,Fpatches of mist and fog forming once
OL,9,Fmore. A warm night for most.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAny early fog clearing to
OL,12,Fleave a hot and sunny day across the
OL,13,Fregion. Light winds and high UV levels
OL,14,Fexpected. A very warm evening and
OL,15,Fnight to come too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
