OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fdry, sunny and very warm throughout
OL,7,Fthe weekend. An increased breeze may
OL,8,Fallow things to feel slightly cooler
OL,9,Fat times. Perhaps a few showers come
OL,10,FMonday. Nights remaining warm.
